
1. install 64bit gcc/ld/objcopy
eg) x86_64-pc-elf-gcc, x86_64-pc-linux-ld, x86_64-pc-linux-objcopy

2. modify GCC64, LD64, OBJCOPY64 variables in Makefile

3. install nasm v2.0 or more recent version

4. necessary utilities: gtags, nm, objdump

5. run ./configure

6. run make

7. check floppy.img, disasm.txt system.map in image directory
